      • commit

        public Resource commit()
                throws InvalidDDMSException
        Description copied from interface: IBuilder
        Finalizes the data gathered for this builder instance. If no values have been provided, a null instance will be returned instead of a possibly invalid one or an empty one.
        Specified by:
